      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a purist\u2019s specification featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This power plant utilizes six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that has been recently serviced for peak volumetric efficiency. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip rear differential. The chassis remains composed with reinforced subframe mounting points and a suspension setup that retains its factory-intended kinematics. While showing light honest wear reflective of its driver-status, the throttle response and linear power delivery remain uncompromising. A well-sorted example ready for the twisties.",
